narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: General writing skills, literary techniques, close reading
In taking this course I greatly improved my writing and was exposed to readings I would not have otherwise explored

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: This course was very helpful in developing writing skills. The discussions held in class on readings were very interesting and the class critiques of papers were very productive. The readings were very engaging, although in most classes we were not able to get to every assigned reading

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: It's a good class and you learn writing skills, so yes.
I would recommend this course to any student interested in improving their writing
